## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent biases present in opinion pieces and public forums. Additionally, the legal landscape surrounding abortion is continually evolving, which may affect the relevance of some findings over time. The report also does not cover all possible perspectives, such as religious or cultural viewpoints, which could provide additional insights into the debate.

